{"tha-ap258:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap258:0.2":"Thomakavagga ","tha-ap258:0.3":"Upahanadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap258:1.1":"“Ahosim candano nama, ","tha-ap258:1.2":"sambuddhassatrajo tada; ","tha-ap258:1.3":"Ekopahano maya dinno, ","tha-ap258:1.4":"bodhim sampajja me tuvam. ","tha-ap258:2.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap258:2.2":"yam panadhim dadim tada; ","tha-ap258:2.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap258:2.4":"upahanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap258:3.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap258:3.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap258:3.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap258:4.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma upahanadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap258:5.1":"Upahanadayakattherassapadanam chattham. "}